                    <h2>Giannis Konstantinidis</h2>
                    <h3>Mozilla</h3>
                    <p>Giannis Konstantinidis was born in Thessaloniki, Greece. He is currently an undergraduate student at the Dept. of Information & Communication Systems Engineering of the University of the Aegean in Samos island, Greece and also a freelance front-end web developer. For the last seven years, Giannis has been part of several free & open source communities, including the Fedora Project and Mozilla, where he has made multiple contributions. In total, he has contributed to more than twelve separate projects.
Giannis loves traveling both domestically and abroad in order to participate at conferences and events. Within his university he helps drive certain community and project related efforts.</p>
